<HEAD>Milan Theater Unveils New Opera Season</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MILAN, Italy (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The prestigious La Scala theater will open
its new season Dec. 7 with the six-hour opera William Tell,
officials said Tuesday.
   La Scala officials said the season will include five new
productions.
   They said it will be preceded by a Sept. 17-26 tour in which the
company will perform some of the most popular operas of Giuseppe
Verdi and Giacomo Puccini in Seoul, during the Olympic Games, and
