<2ND_LINE>BC-WKD--Angell, Adv 29-31-1st ld-Writethru, b0873,0955</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>$Adv29</NOTE>
<NOTE>$Adv30</NOTE>
<NOTE>$Adv31</NOTE>
